common_2020_mushi_010_mushi_01:
Hello there! My name is Katy, and I am the owner
of Patisserie Soapberry.[npcn:16]
common_2020_mushi_010_mushi_02:
Oh? The new Champion everybody is talking
about—is it actually you, sweetie?[npcn:16]
common_2020_mushi_010_mushi_03:
Hurray! I guessed correctly! I suppose that makes
sense, though. You sure were strong![npcn:16]
common_2020_mushi_010_mushi_04:
You really looked like you were enjoying yourself
when you tried my sweet treats, too.\c
People like that always have great potential.[npcn:16]
common_2020_mushi_010_mushi_05:
So you’re here on an errand for the Top
Champion, are you?[npcn:16]
common_2020_mushi_010_mushi_06:
I had completely forgotten that she was
supposed to be going around for inspections![npcn:16]
common_2020_mushi_010_mushi_07:
Thankfully, I just happened to be here today to
give cakes to my staff. Phew. Lucky me![npcn:16]
common_2020_mushi_010_mushi_08:
Very well, then. Is it time for me to get a taste of
our new Champion’s strength?[npcn:16]
common_2020_mushi_010_mushi_retry:
Oh? Are you here to let me have a taste of our
new Champion’s strength?[npcn:16]
common_2020_mushi_010_mushi_09:
Hehe. Oh, what fun! Let’s go somewhere more
suited for battling.[npcn:16]
common_2020_mushi_010_mushi_10:
Awww. Not yet? Do come back when you’re
good and ready![npcn:16]
